        </item>
        <item>
            <title>小鹏汽车香港盛大活动全新 X9 亮相    CEO 何小鹏现身发布会，展示全系列电动车</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/xpeng-global-brand-night/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=xpeng-global-brand-night</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/xpeng-global-brand-night/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 16 Apr 2025 04:00:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[X9]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[XPENG]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小鹏]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小鹏汇天]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[自动泊车]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遥控泊车]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[飞天车]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1303455</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div dir="auto">XPENG 小鹏汽车在香港首次举利「小鹏全球热爱之夜」品牌活动，厂方邀请了全球超过 500 位记者及本地的 VIP 车主到场参与，会上除展出小鹏全线电动车系及最新技术外，更发表全新 2025 款小鹏 X9 旗舰七座 MPV 新车，小鹏汽车创办人何小鹏更亲自到场发表演说，分享公司旗下的电动车、飞天车、机械人及 AI 汽车的发展趋势。</div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303489" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_184106-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_184106-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_184106-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto">XPENG 于展德邮轮码头展出了品牌旗下全系列逾 20 款最新电动车，当中包括最新推出的 2025 款 X9、P7+、G6、G9 及 M03 等。此外，同场亦展出了小鹏汇天「陆地航母」飞天车、让用户可以率先体验全自动泊车及手机遥控泊车等崭新功能。同场亦划分了多个不同展区，让在场人士体验 X9 在不同主题下宽敞车箱空间在精心布置下的可朔性、及 X9 中排零重力座椅的体验区。会上厂方人员透露 X9 已通过运输署检验遥控泊车功能，相信很快可以透过 OTA 更新为车身庞大的 X9 车主提供这个方便实用的功能。</div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303491" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_190523-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_190523-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_190523-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto" style="text-align: center;">小鹏汽车创办人何小鹏亲自到场发表长达演说</div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303494" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_171216-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_171216-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_171216-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303488" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_185004-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_185004-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_185004-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303485" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_185744-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_185744-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_185744-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303498" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_172836-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_172836-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_172836-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto">2025 最新版本的 X9 七座电动 MPV 外型上没有太大变动，主要针对车箱空间及舒适性进行升级，当中包括新设计的两张中排座椅加入一键零重力模式、同时备有手机无线功能、及座位上金属质感的功能面板等等。新版 X9 「一换一」车价分别为标准版 HK$599,900(84.5kWh 标准版) 及长续航版 HK$639,900(101.5kWh 长续航版) 起，分别可以提供 500km 及 590km 续航力（WLTP 标准）。此外，厂方亦提供包括豪华内装套装的限量 Phantom Edition 版本，售价为 HK$679,900 起。</div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303496" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_171010-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_171010-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_171010-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto" style="text-align: center;">虽然未有提供试飞，不过小鹏汇天「陆地航母」飞天车亦是场中另一焦点</div><div dir="auto"></div><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
